spec_data.Name: geany-plugins-treebrowser
spec_data.Description:
The tree browser plugin for Geany provides an alternate way to browse through
your files. It displays files and directories in a tree view and has more
features than the file browser plugin delivered with Geany itself.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 03 Aug 2017 09:28:03 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Alternate file browser plugin providing a tree view of directories
